These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: drama, family, spy, action, sports
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, video-games, board-games, magic-tricks, singing
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in the middle##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching drama movies is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
6. the person watching sports movies is in the middle##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
8. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Movie-Genre          | family | drama | sports | action | spy |
| Hobby   | board-games  | singing      | magic-tricks   | dancing     | video-games    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  dressmaker, social-worker, project-manager, coach, fisherman
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, june, july, february, november
1. the dressmaker is in an even position##4
2. the dressmaker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the fisherman is in the middle##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left or right of the fisherman##3
5. the person who's birthday is in september is between the project-manager and the person who's birthday is in february##2
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the dressmaker##1
7. the project-manager is on the left of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Job   | project-manager     | coach       | fisherman    | dressmaker | social-worker   |
| Birthday      | june | september | february | november      | july |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
House: futuristic, wooden, palace, cottage, art-deco
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: rugby, soccer, tennis, parkour, golf
1. the person who's sport is parkour is the futuristic house##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
4. the wooden house is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
7. the palace house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
8. the art-deco house is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| House         | futuristic | palace | wooden | cottage    | art-deco |
| Sport   | parkour     | rugby        | tennis      | soccer | golf      |

