.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
5 different games are played: whist, monopoly, poker, backgammon, billiard
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: zinnia, balloon-flower, daffodil, marigold, amaryllis
1. the person playing poker is in the middle##1
2. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the far right##1
4. the person playing billiard is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person playing monopoly is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person playing billiard##2
7. the person who growsamaryllis is the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Game         | whist      | backgammon | poker | monopoly   | billiard  |
| Flower   | marigold | amaryllis    | daffodil        | zinnia | balloon-flower |

