2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
7. the person who's hobby is singing is in an even position##4
8. the person driving the car is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Transport      | boat      | skateboard | motorbike   | ship  | car  |
| Hobby   | dancing | camping | collecting | singing | board-games |

