.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, zombie, thriller, epic, martial-arts
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae, blues, techno, hip-hop
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
2. the fan of reggae is between the fan of hip-hop and the person watching thriller movies##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
5. the fan of blues is the person watching thriller movies##1
6. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
7. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
8. the fan of techno is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie        | animation                | epic  | thriller  | martial-arts            |
| Music-Genre        | dubstep | hip-hop | reggae | blues | techno |

