.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
House: art-deco, wooden, modern, farmhouse, cape-cod
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, tulip, orchid, sunflower, lily
1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
2. the person who growslily is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
3. the wooden house is in the middle##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
5. the person who growsorchid is in an odd position##4
6. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
7. the person who growsazalea is on the left or right of the cape-cod house##3
8. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
9. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| House   | cape-cod       | modern   | wooden    | farmhouse    | art-deco |
| Flower        | orchid | azalea | tulip | lily | sunflower     |

