.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-8::.
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, subway, roller, jet-ski, taxi
5 different games are played: monopoly, chess, poker, scrabble, billiard
1. the person playing poker is the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing monopoly is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing billiard##2
6. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing chess##1
7. the person playing poker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Transport      | roller  | boat       | subway      | jet-ski  | taxi   |
| Game   | billiard | monopoly | scrabble | chess | poker |

