.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, electronic, country, indie, soul
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, july, april, september, may
1. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
2. the fan of indie is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of indie is on the far right##1
5. the fan of electronic is the person who's birthday is in march##1
6. the fan of country is between the fan of electronic and the fan of dubstep##2
7. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the fan of country##1
8. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Music-Genre   | soul | electronic | country     | dubstep | indie |
| Birthday           | july | march     | april | may    | september      |

