3. the person playing poker is the person who likes fuchsia##1
4. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person who likes fuchsia##1
5. the person playing mah-jongg is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
7. the person who likes ivory is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Color     | lavender | grey | ivory | fuchsia | emerald |
| Game   | snooker | monopoly | mah-jongg    | poker    | billiard  |

