.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
City: edinburgh, nizza, london, liverpool, miami
There are 5 different favourite beverages: sprite, almond-milk, tea, hot-chocolate, cola
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person drinking tea and the person drinking almond-milk##2
4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking cola is the person traveling to london##1
6. the person drinking cola is in an odd position##4
7. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| City    | nizza    | miami  | edinburgh      | liverpool     | london |
| Beverage   | sprite | almond-milk | hot-chocolate | tea | cola |

