.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: fishing, camping, gardening, puzzles, reading
There are 5 different nationalities: british, canadian, brazilian, italian, chinese
1. the canadian is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the chinese is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the chinese is in the middle##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
5. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3
6. the british is between the chinese and the person who's hobby is camping##2
7. the canadian is in an odd position##4
8. the canadian is on the far left##1
9. the chinese is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Hobby        | puzzles | reading | fishing  | gardening | camping     |
| Nationality   | canadian  | brazilian     | chinese | british      | italian |

