5. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
6. the person driving the motorbike is between the person watching comedy movies and the person driving the skateboard##2
7. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
