.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
5 different games are played: bridge, whist, mah-jongg, chess, go
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, lizard, horse, frog
1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
2. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the person playing chess##3
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing whist##3
7. the owner of the lizard is in an odd position##4
8. the owner of the horse is in the middle##1
9. the owner of the fish is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Game   | whist  | mah-jongg    | chess | bridge   | go |
| Pet   | frog | fish | horse    | chinchilla | lizard |

