5. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person eating kale##3
7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |    3     |    4     |   5    |
