.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
5 different games are played: poker, backgammon, billiard, snooker, monopoly
There are 5 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate, coffee, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is in an even position##4
3. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
6. the person drinking cola is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
8. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
9. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Game   | poker | backgammon | monopoly     | billiard | snooker |
| Beverage     | coffee       | mirinda   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk   | cola        |

