.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-19::.
5 different games are played: billiard, domino, backgammon, snooker, canasta
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, scooter, car, roller, jet-ski
1. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the car is the person driving the car##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
5. the person playing canasta is between the person playing billiard and the person driving the jet-ski##2
6. the person driving the scooter is between the person playing snooker and the person driving the jet-ski##2
7. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
8. the person driving the jet-ski is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Game         | snooker | backgammon | domino | canasta | billiard     |
| Transport   | roller    | scooter   | jet-ski       | car | taxi |

