.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
There are 5 different nationalities: american, british, mexican, chinese, pakistani
There are 5 different favourite colors: ebony, white, light-blue, turquise, fuchsia
1. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the pakistani##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the pakistani##1
3. the person who likes white is between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes turquise##2
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the pakistani##1
5. the chinese is in the middle##1
6. the person who likes fuchsia is the american##1
7. the british is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Nationality   | american | mexican      | chinese | pakistani     | british      |
| Color     | fuchsia | white | turquise | ebony | light-blue |

 